Package: libvlc5
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: libvlccore5
Description: VLC media run-time
 This package includes the core LibVLC media framework library.

Package: libvlc-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libvlc5 (= ${binary:Version})
Provides: libvlccore-dev, libvlc5-dev, libvlccore5-dev
Description: development files for VLC media player
 Install this if you want to build bindings or external plugins for VLC.

Package: libvlc5-dbg
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Priority: extra
Depends: libvlc5 (= ${binary:Version})
Provides: libvlccore5-dbg, vlc-dbg
Description: debug symbols for VLC media player
 Install this if you want to debug VLC media player.

Package: vlc-player
Architecture: any
Section: graphics
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: VLC media player
 VLC media player is a versatile multimedia player for various audio and video
 formats (MPEG, DivX, H.264, MP3, Xiph, Flash, ...) and streaming protocols.
 .
 This package includes the VLC media player, but it lacks streaming output
 to save space on your device. Install this if you do not need to stream,
 record or transcode with your device.

Package: vlc-streamer
Architecture: any
Section: graphics
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, vlc-player (= ${binary:Version})
Description: VLC encoding and streaming
 VLC media player is a versatile multimedia player for various audio and video
 formats (MPEG, DivX, H.264, MP3, Xiph, Flash, ...) and streaming protocols.
 .
 This package includes the streaming and encoding functionality of the
 VLC media player.

Package: vlc-weird
Architecture: any
Section: graphics
Priority: extra
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, vlc-player (= ${binary:Version})
Description: VLC weird plugins
 VLC media player is a versatile multimedia player for various audio and video
 formats (MPEG, DivX, H.264, MP3, Xiph, Flash, ...) and streaming protocols.
 .
 This package includes various official VLC plugins which are not normally
 useful on a mobile handsets.
